# ─── Security: Firebase / GCP service-account credentials ────────────────────
# Never commit service-account JSON files.
# Place your renamed key (firebase-key.json) inside backend-api/ locally;
# it will be ignored by Git automatically via the rule below.
backend-api/*.json

# Also ignore any env files that may carry secrets
backend-api/.env
.env
